ON> Kansas </LOCATION> <LOCATION> City </LOCATION>. The fares previously were $ 43. Midway officials waived minimum-stay requirements that usually apply to discount tickets, but said the reduced-rate tickets must be purchased by Jan. 20 and travel completed by March 31. <ORGANIZATION> United </ORGANIZATION>, the main holding of <ORGANIZATION> UAL </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Corp. </ORGANIZATION>, did not specify whether its fares would have minimum-stay requirements or expiration dates.
